text: Katie Lynn Leclerc (born November 6, 1986) is an American actress. She plays a coffee lover in the 2014 movie Caffeinated. Also in 2014, she played Katie in The Ones. Leclerc was born in San Antonio, Texas and grew up in Lakewood, Colorado. ==References== Category:Actors from Colorado Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from San Antonio, Texas Category:1986 births Category:Living people
